# Input

```scss
.theme{
  spacing:(1px+2px)*3{
    size:1px;
  }

  palette:map.get($colors,primary){
    family:red;
  }
}

```


# Formatted

```scss
.theme {
	spacing: (1px + 2px) * 3 {
		size: 1px;
	}

	palette: map.get($colors, primary) {
		family: red;
	}
}

```
